{{der-top|Compounds}}
* {{ja-r|甄陶|けんとう}}: to [[mold]] as [[clay]], to [[shape]] something; to [[educate]]
* {{ja-r|甄別|けんべつ}}: to [[examine]] something closely
* {{ja-r|甄揚|けんよう}}: to make one's [[reputation]] clear to the world at large and thereby build up one's [[prestige]]
* {{ja-r|甄録|けんろく}}: to [[clearly]] [[write]] something down, to [[record]] with [[clarity]]
